{
  "stem": "24462.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I was starting, you know, in the-- taking samples in the factory from diffident stages of production, brought to laboratory, checked it for sugar, for starch, and contents for water, and things like that, whatever.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the afternoon, 6 o'clock, I went home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had everything-- all the meals prepared by the [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Shultzes ?] family.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I paid them an amount which was half of my wages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was approximately the amount for everything, lodging and full board.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the rest of the money, I could only play cards or nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You couldn't buy anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But in the meantime, in the factory, I developed a very good relationship with a few Poles, which are working, and with the French.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was ?] quite a group of French prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The prisoner-- the French prisoners of war were living in a camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were coming to the factory without any guards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "No point of running away, because there was no where to run away without clothing, without language, without nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The-- the best thing was to live in the camp, because camp was quite comfortable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The Red Cross parcels start coming end of '42, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The post was working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The communication with family was by letters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So it wasn't so bad to-- to wait another year or two and to be released instead of running away and who knows where.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the French prisoners of war, I had a very good relationship with [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Robert ?] and other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had pictures together somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we started some commerce.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were getting everything except fresh bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because fresh bread, they needed everyday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Biscuits and things were not-- not good enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
